{
  "stem": "14867.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he saw that I'm really serious about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he finally said, all right, I'll bring-- they paid for my trip, of course.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they paid the lawyer because they wanted to accelerate it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so then the telephone started to go back and forth, and [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Feliks, ?] in the beginning, was very apprehensive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Finally, I said, you will come, and also for a month.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we extended my visit visa for another two months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he came, and we got married in my uncle's house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- and that's also then we stayed in New York.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And Feliks, right away, went to work, and had a very good position, and I worked.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then we had to leave for Montreal, for Canada, because if you come for a visit, you cannot stay.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You have to leave the country and ask for a re-entry, apply again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it took us two years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we finally-- also, my uncle worked very hard on it because it was a very, very difficult at that time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was not a displaced person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had the Polish passport.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was much more difficult.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Polish quota was more difficult to get in, under Polish quota.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, again, both of us went to work and saved a little bit of money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I told you I had a friend who helped us with a loan to-- in the bank.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we felt if we buy a farm, [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Feliks ?] will be able to work better.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I'll work for a while.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "What kind of work did [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Feliks ?] do when you first came here?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He, first of all, he painted, and then he did commercial-- commercial art.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
